<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Verify your sign-up</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Mono:wght@500&display=swap');

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #f5f5f3;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    .wrapper {
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 48px auto;
      padding: 0 16px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #e8e8e4;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .accent-bar {
      height: 3px;
      background: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .card-body {
      padding: 48px 40px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .brand {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .brand-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      background: #1a1a1a;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .brand-name {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 300;
      max-width: 340px;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
    }

    .otp-container {
      background: #f8f8f6;
      border: 1px solid #e8e8e4;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 28px 48px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      display: inline-block;
      min-width: 200px;
    }

    .otp-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #a0a0a0;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .otp-code {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .expiry-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      background: #f0f0ec;
      border-radius: 100px;
      padding: 5px 14px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .expiry-dot {
      width: 5px;
      height: 5px;
      background: #6b6b6b;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .expiry-text {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b6b6b;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: #e8e8e4;
      margin: 0 -40px 28px;
    }

    .footer-note {
      font-size: 12.5px;
      color: #9b9b9b;
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-weight: 300;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="accent-bar"></div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h1>Verify Your Email</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
         Hi <%= name %>, We received a sign-up request for your account. Use the code below to complete verification.
        </p>
        <div class="otp-container">
          <div class="otp-label">One-time code</div>
          <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
          <div class="expiry-badge">
            <span class="expiry-text">Expires in 2 minutes</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p class="footer-note">
          If you did not attempt to sign up, you can safely ignore this email.
          This code will become invalid after use or expiry.
        </p>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
